<h1>Audit (A-07-12-00397)</h1>

<h2>06-06-2013<br />
Blue Cross Blue Shield of Georgia Overstated Its Medicare Segment Pension Assets and Understated Medicare's Share of the Excess Liabilities as of May 31, 2009</h2>

<h2 class="line">Complete Report</h2>

<p class="download">Download the 

<a href="/oas/reports/region7/71200397.pdf" target="_blank">complete report</a>

<!-- Footer -->
<!--#include virtual="/layout/pdf_inline.asp" -->
