<h2 class="line">Summary</h2>

<p>Blue Cross Blue Shield of Georgia (BCBSGA), a terminated Medicare contractor, overstated the Medicare segment pension assets as of May 31, 2009, by $13,000.  In addition, BCBSGA understated Medicare's share of excess pension liabilities by $9,000 as a result of the segment closing adjustment on May 31, 2009. </p>




<p>Copies can also be obtained by contacting the Office of Public Affairs at <a href="mailto:Public.Affairs@oig.hhs.gov">Public.Affairs@oig.hhs.gov</a>.	</p>		

